          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 4------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->
      <div class="row align-items-center py-4 py-xl-5 my-2">
        <div class="col-md-6 pb-2 mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <Image class="rounded-5" src={dataVisualisation} alt="Image" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-5 offset-xl-1">
          <div class="ps-md-4 pe-xl-0">
            <h2 class="h1 pb-2 pb-lg-3" style="color:white">
              Data Visualisation
            </h2>
            <p
              class="pb-2 pb-lg-0 mb-3 mb-lg-3"
              style="color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)"
            >
              Data Visualisation is story telling with a purpose. Data
              Visualisation is an art and we treat is such. We donâ€™t treat data
              visualisation as just a data problems, we understand that visuals
              are for humans.
            </p>
            <div class="row row-cols-2">
              <div class="col">
                <div
                  class="d-table rounded-1 p-2 mb-3"
                  style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);"
                >
                  <Image
                    class="d-block d-dark-mode-none m-1"
                    src={thumbsUp}
                    width="28"
                    alt="Icon"
                  />
                </div>
                <h3 class="h5 mb-2" style="color:white">Ease of Use</h3>
                <p class="fs-sm mb-0" style="color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)">
                  Interactive and Intuitive data , designed for business users.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col">
                <div
                  class="d-table rounded-1 p-2 mb-3"
                  style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);"
                >
                  <Image
                    class="d-block d-dark-mode-none m-1"
                    src={handShake}
                    width="28"
                    alt="Icon"
                  />
                </div>
                <h3 class="h5 mb-2" style="color:white">Collaborative</h3>
                <p class="fs-sm mb-0" style="color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)">
                  Build to enable collaboration between business and IT.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a
              href="#"
              style="border:solid 1px rgba(47, 183, 184, 1); border-radius:8px; 
            padding: 12px 28px; text-decoration:none; 
            position:relative; top:2rem;"
